OL,7,FThis is reduced from the current
OL,8,Fqualifying period of 24 months.
OL,10,FThe legislation has been caught in a
OL,11,Fstand-off between peers and MPs over
OL,12,Fthe government's plan to give workers
OL,13,Fprotection on their first day in a
OL,14,Fjob, as well as measures to ban
OL,15,F"exploitative" zero-hours contracts.
