OL,7,FIn an update on Thursday, the
OL,8,FDepartment for Business and Trade
OL,9,F(DBT) said: "The government convened a
OL,10,Fseries of constructive conversations
OL,11,Fbetween trade unions and business
OL,12,Frepresentatives.
OL,14,F"On the basis of the outcome of these
OL,15,Fdiscussions, the Government will now
OL,16,Fmove forward on the issue of unfair
OL,17,Fdismissal protections in the
OL,18,FEmployment Rights Bill to ensure it
OL,19,Fcan reach royal assent and keep to the
OL,20,FGovernment's published delivery
OL,21,Ftimeline."
