OL,5,Cdismissal
OL,7,FIt went on: "The discussions concluded
OL,8,Fthat reducing the qualifying period
OL,9,Ffor unfair dismissal from 24 months to
OL,10,Fsix months (whilst maintaining
OL,11,Fexisting day-one protection against
OL,12,Fdiscrimination and automatically
OL,13,Funfair grounds for dismissal) is a
OL,14,Fworkable package."
OL,16,FThe government insisted the amended
OL,17,Fpackage would "benefit millions of
OL,18,Fworking people who will gain new
OL,19,Frights and offer business and
OL,20,Femployers much-needed clarity".
