OL,7,F"To further strengthen these
OL,8,Fprotections, the Government has
OL,9,Fcommitted to ensure that the unfair
OL,10,Fdismissal qualifying period can only
OL,11,Fbe varied by primary legislation and
OL,12,Fthat the compensation cap will be
OL,13,Flifted," the DBT said.
OL,15,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak said
OL,16,Fthe "absolute priority" was to get the
OL,17,Flegislation on to the statute books.
